Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:12.20,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Please watch your step"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give him something to eat today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The next stop is just ahead.\NJust sit down and wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,People were being burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Call 110! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the police officer?\NThere were people!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, so someone\Nwas being burned, were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your typical flames don't\Nburn things up so completely
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that they don't leave any debris behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure you didn't dream it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,These scorches are from where
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,some homeless guy\Nbuilt a fire or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:59.72,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is there no final{\i}\N{\i1}piece to unravel this puzzle?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:07.10,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wander around the search area with dread{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:14.48,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With shaky self-confidence{\i}\N{\i1}facing unyielding damnation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:18.28,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still alive, but I can't catch up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:24.54,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to residual images of hidden memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:28.79,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let loose dark shame unbounded{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:32.54,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the ends of this world of kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:36.67,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even hopes best forgotten are silenced{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:40.39,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as corruption spreads out before our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.64,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Consign it to darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:47.31,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An ego on trial{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:58.49,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a moment of hesitation is seen ecstasy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.03,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\be6\an8}"Episode 1 'God's Great Judgment'"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Full point! Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Th-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you very much!\N- Th-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.60,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Fortitude and Vigor"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Full point! Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurakoji, thanks so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,for spending time with\Nour meager little club here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The training of the club's\Nmembers is truly eye-opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurakoji sure is fantastic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's usually so neat and smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but when you see her doing {\i1}aikido,{\i}\Nshe really looks cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of which,\Nshe always earns top grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could have Sakurakoji as my girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't care if the\Nwhole world turned against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo-hoo! Good morning, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A good morning to you, Aoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sakura?\NYou seem kind of glum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is no special matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Miss Kanda! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Takatsu, Sakurakoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is a transfer student\Nwho will be in our class starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ogami Rei.\NIt's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.72,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ogami Rei"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold the phone!\NOgami's pretty handsome, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a cool and somewhat\Nmysterious air about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,High points!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For reasons having\Nto do with his parents' work,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami is moving here by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's all make him\Nfeel welcome, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no mistake,\Nthat is him... the boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...from last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Overseas, huh?\NYou must have rocking English!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What countries did you go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in Europe a lot for the last few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Sakura?\NTaking an interest in Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Miss Sakurakoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to speak to you alone.\NCome along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrible news!\NSakurakoji is gonna declare her love
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to the transfer student!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't believe it!\N- No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't believe it!\N- My dream bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura is amazing! How bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But those two would make the\Nperfect couple, wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- So, what did you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- I shall ask you point-blank.\N- So, what did you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you and\Nwhat were you doing last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was at my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job? Then I ask you, using that glove,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,are you not concealing the burns you received
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,last night in the park when\Nyou killed and burned those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? I can't hear them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? If I am wrong, then remove the glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no burns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a good-luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a child,\NI once hurt someone with this hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain someone gave me this,\Nto make sure it never happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, I apologize for having kept you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can be friends\Ngoing forward, as classmates,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on! Sakura, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm, this is an unexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...he turned you down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He what?! He rejected Sakurakoji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are, Ogami Rei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible for\Nhim to cause Sakura grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami! You've turned\Nthe whole world against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This is exasperating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I shall not give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... Sakura, this is the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been so wrapped up in a boy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, I shall uncover the truth about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I have to say, no matter how often I see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,your way of eating is so charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are infatuated, huh, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I cannot afford to take my eyes from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm. Ogami seems so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise that\Nyou'd be interested in him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, he eluded me, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the culprit returns\Nto the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall wait here for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Were there truly people burned here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that some phantasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat this. I am sorry\NI brought you naught yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When that old man\Ngave you food, he would do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not ready to\Ntake a liking to me, already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, you talk\Nlike that to everyone, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I was just thinking,\Nit's the firm tone of a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What, are you saying it does not fit my image?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was thinking,\Nit's cool how you're not submissive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"C-Cool" is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am just a little...\NMy family is a bit odd, is all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that dog is quite timid around people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You just didn't have\Nenough trust in people, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Please, don't lick me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami seems so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can be friends, as classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not a bad chap, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji,\Nwhat is this dog's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dog."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... a nice name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a stray?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Her master,\Na homeless old man... was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit is a group known as G-Falcon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to call themselves that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the falcon tattoos they\Nall wear on their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When this group commits their crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the gang that is over\Nthem keeps everything hushed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what Father says.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence no one can bring them to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the police pretend to see them not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take\Nrevenge against these culprits?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to take up justice,\Nand bring the hammer down on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:12:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... That old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He lived without anyone knowing him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,then died without anyone knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It is something I cannot abide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji,\Nyou can always remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the rest of the world forgets him,\Nyou can remember him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not forget. No matter what, not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need the laws\Nof this country to judge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye;\Na tooth for a tooth; evil for evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Code of Hammurabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The "evil for evil"\Npart is gratuitous, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally smiled for me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe you had taken a disliking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for that, Ogami.\NI had my doubts about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What has become of Ogami Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,His placement is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains is for\Nhim to begin, Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm, good. All according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming it wasn't Ogami,\Nthen what exactly was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a phantasm, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, want to come\Nwith us for some karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura is coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have something to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who do you think I'm doing this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "huh" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I have to work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, now that you mention it,\Nwhat work do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a cleaner. A trash man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Most admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? It looks like\Nthey're already calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is this?!\NAll of a sudden, you're on close terms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing especially\Nirregular about our contact, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, no way,\Nthat's a hyper-fast connection!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about today's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take out the trash, just as was planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to\Ndo about Sakurakoji Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to do much of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I was always going to,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eliminate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When will you finally take a liking to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, we haven't\Nbeen able to reach our pals
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,since two nights ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys hang out here, right?\NI'm asking you if you've seen anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know anything, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just dialed 110!\NThe police will arrive here shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The police? Oh, right, the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Falcon tattoos... Then they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Falcon! The group\Nthat killed that old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Young lady, you shouldn't go\Nsticking your nose into everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just concerned about\Nsome of our pals that vanished here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They vanished... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it, young lady?\NYou know something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it two nights ago that\Nyou say your pals vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!\N- Is she in on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you really\Ndo know something. Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, why don't you\Ntell me everything you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Two nights ago... they vanished...\NThen it {\i1}did{\i} happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you mumbling to yourself about?\NTell us what you know, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I know it\Nreally happened, that will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing more to say to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you little!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-w-w-w!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn yourselves in to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't answer us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll just have\Nto beat it out of you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My body won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take this belt! Tie her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid girl. You could\Nhave left the homeless guy alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but you tried to help him,\Nand this is what you get!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! It's dog soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm open! I'm open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here, I'm passing!\N- I'm open! I'm open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, already!\NShe has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You will face me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this any time to\Nbe worrying about a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait! I will get\Nyou to a hospital right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pesky girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna get pummeled that badly,\Nthen you'll have your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All you want, after you answer us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your organs, and many of your bones...\NThere's no saving you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that you're still alive at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to protect\NMiss Sakurakoji, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami! Hurry and get her to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I will put you out of your misery now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami... You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You killed it, did you?\NThat's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill it, it won't respond,\Nand where's the fun in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye; a tooth for a tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and evil for evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's started, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for you, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What? My job as a trash man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you one final question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you turn yourselves in to be judged,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or would you rather die here?\NWhich will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you! {\i1}You're{\i} the one who's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well then, die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye;\Na tooth for a tooth; evil for evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami... Then it really was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as classmates that\NI said I hoped we could be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:22:01.55,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you, too, will know{\i}\N{\i1}where that white crow is heading{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:07.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We fly through the brilliant city,{\i}\N{\i1}unnoticed by all around{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:21.82,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking only for a reason to live{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:27.07,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ashamed of our hollow selves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:32.03,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should we just laugh and go along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:37.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the rules the world has decided on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:42.34,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stripped bare, following{\i}\N{\i1}wherever our instincts lead{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:46.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the truth from{\i}\N{\i1}which we've averted our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:51.18,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Verdicts handed down for no one's sake{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:55.97,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cast off the dark robes and get on your feet{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:00.73,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure white wishes become our wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:05.28,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shake off your hesitations now, and fly high{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:13.87,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have no fear; the answers{\i}\N{\i1}lie beyond the darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, "Code: Breaker" episode 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Spiral Blue Flower, Blossoming in Flame."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I will burn everything up,\Nuntil the end of my life!
